Title: 整体架构图
Describe: 覆盖 S04_ARCHITECTURE。展示分层边界、运行时依赖、发布边界和测试/配置数据如何反馈到实现。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S04_ARCHITECTURE - 分层和发布边界

[Description]
LangChain Python 的架构是“轻 core + 活跃高层包 + partner 实现 + 标准测试 + 配置数据生成”。`langchain-core` 明确说明不包含第三方 integrations；`langchain` 活跃包把 agent 编排交给 LangGraph；partners 作为独立发布包接入 OpenAI、Anthropic、Ollama、Qdrant 等 provider；`langchain-tests` 给 chat model、embeddings、tools 等实现提供一致性测试；`langchain-profiles` 生成 provider model profile 数据。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
frame "用户代码" as UserRuntime {
  component "init_chat_model" as InitAPI
  component "create_agent" as AgentAPI
}
frame "LangChain packages" as LangChainPackages {
  component "langchain-core\nRunnable, messages, tools, models" as Core
  component "langchain\nagents and chat_models" as Active
  component "langchain-classic\nlegacy chains and adapters" as Classic
}
frame "Integration packages" as IntegrationPackages {
  component "langchain-openai" as OpenAI
  component "langchain-anthropic" as Anthropic
  component "other partners" as OtherPartners
}
frame "Quality and data" as Quality {
  component "langchain-tests" as Tests
  component "langchain-profiles CLI" as Profiles
  component "GitHub Actions" as Actions
}
component "LangGraph" as LangGraph
component "Provider SDKs and APIs" as ProviderAPIs
UserRuntime --> Active : imports public API
Active --> Core : uses abstractions
Active --> LangGraph : compiles agent graph
Active --> IntegrationPackages : imports selected provider
Classic --> Core : legacy compatibility
OpenAI --> Core : implements contracts
Anthropic --> Core : implements contracts
OtherPartners --> Core : implement contracts
IntegrationPackages --> ProviderAPIs : network calls
Tests --> IntegrationPackages : conformance checks
Profiles --> IntegrationPackages : generated capability data
Actions --> LangChainPackages : package jobs
Actions --> IntegrationPackages : partner jobs
@enduml

[Detail]
从“用户代码”读起，箭头表示运行时 import、调用或质量反馈。`init_chat_model` 和 `create_agent` 是最常见入口；它们不直接把 provider SDK 逻辑放进 core，而是按 provider 名称加载 integration 包。`langchain-classic` 位于旧兼容层，文件量最大，应该避免承载新功能。`langchain-tests` 和 `model-profiles` 是架构的质量回路：前者检查实现行为是否符合 core 契约，后者把 provider 能力数据集中生成。维护风险集中在 core 抽象变更、agent graph 边条件、provider profile 与 SDK 实际能力不一致。
